      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty to believe it\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it is in absolutely pristine condition inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh car feel. I'm really looking for it to go to a home where it'll be just as loved as it was here. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
