    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade E46 M3 in pristine, collector-quality condition. Power is delivered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a factory-spec 8,000 RPM redline. This example features a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and the M Variable Differential Lock for superior mechanical grip. Critically, the VANOS system has been overhauled and the rear subframe proactively reinforced to exceed factory durability. With a concours-level engine bay, immaculate bushings, and a flawless undercarriage, this M3 offers a precise, analog driving experience with zero deferred maintenance. A turn-key masterpiece for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 47900.0,
