    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'pre-owned.' This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, appearing exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections\u2014no stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of creasing or bolster wear, and the interior still retains that distinct factory-fresh scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions with absolute precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule exclusively at authorized dealerships with a complete service history included. Driven sparingly and never in inclement weather, this vehicle offers a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands perfection. It drives tight, quiet, and powerful, providing a genuine new-car experience.",
      "price": 48500.0,
